      +   '<div style="font-size:13.5px;line-height:1.5">'
      +     'A LYMX admin is reviewing your sign-up details (usually within 24 hours). '
      +     'While we review:'
      +     '<ul style="margin:6px 0 0;padding-left:18px">'
      +       '<li>Your account is active — you can browse, message, edit your profile</li>'
      +       '<li><strong>' + holdLabel + '</strong> is held until we verify</li>'
      +     '</ul>'
      +     '<details style="margin-top:8px;font-size:13px"><summary style="cursor:pointer;color:#92400e;font-weight:700">What is verification, and why?</summary>'
      +     '<div style="margin-top:6px;color:#78350f">LYMX verifies every account before unlocking value transfers (' + holdLabel + ') to prevent fraud, fake signups, and abuse. The review checks your phone number, email, signup source, and IP. Most pass automatically; a small percentage get manual review. If we need anything from you, we email — check your inbox.</div>'
      +     '</details>'
      +   '</div>'
      + '</div></div>';
    banner.style.display = '';
  }
}

